{"title_page": "Plectania", "text_new": "{{Taxobox\n| image = Plectania nannfeldtii 187.jpg\n| image_width = 240px\n| image_caption = ''Plectania nannfeldtii''\n| regnum = [[Fungi]]\n| divisio = [[Ascomycota]]\n| classis = [[Pezizomycetes]]\n| ordo = [[Pezizales]]\n| familia = [[Sarcosomataceae]]\n| genus = '''''Plectania'''''\n| genus_authority = [[Karl Wilhelm Gottlieb Leopold Fuckel|Fuckel]] (1870)\n| type_species = ''[[Plectania melastoma]]''\n| type_species_authority = ([[George Brettingham Sowerby II|Sowerby]]) Fuckel (1870)\n| synonyms_ref = <ref name=\"urlMycoBank: Plectania\"/>\n| synonyms = ''Gloeocalyx'' <small>[[George Edward Massee|Massee]] (1901)</small><br>\n''Peziza'' subgen. ''Rhizopodella'' <small>[[Mordecai Cubitt Cooke|Cooke]] (1879)</small>\n}}\n\n'''''Plectania''''' is a [[genus]] of [[fungi]] in the family [[Sarcosomataceae]]. There are 15 [[species]] in the genus, which have a widespread distribution, especially in northern [[temperate]] areas.<ref name=\"Kirk 2008\"/> ''Plectania'' was circumscribed by German botanist [[Karl Wilhelm Gottlieb Leopold Fuckel]] in 1870.<ref name=\"Fuckel 1870\"/>\n\n==Species==\n*''[[Plectania campylospora|P. campylospora]]''\n*''[[Plectania carranzae|P. carranzae]]''\n*''[[Plectania chilensis|P. chilensis]]''\n*''[[Plectania ericae|P. ericae]]''\n*''[[Plectania mediterranea|P. mediterranea]]''\n*''[[Plectania melaena|P. melaena]]''\n*''[[Plectania megalocrater|P. megalocrater]]''\n*''[[Plectania melastoma|P. melastoma]]''\n*''[[Plectania milleri|P. milleri]]''\n*''[[Plectania nannfeldtii|P. nannfeldtii]]''\n*''[[Plectania platensis|P. platensis]]''\n*''[[Plectania rhytidia|P. rhytidia]]''\n*''[[Plectania rugosa|P. rugosa]]''\n*''[[Plectania seaveri|P. seaveri]]'' (Brazil)<ref name=\"Carbone 2012\"/>\n*''[[Plectania zugazae|P. zugazae]]''\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|refs=\n\n<ref name=\"Carbone 2012\">{{cite journal |vauthors=Carbone M, Agnello C, LaGreca S |title=''Plectania seaveri'' (Ascomycota, Pezizales),